{
  "stem": "1169.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They did not wear a uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had to wear a yellow arm band that you had to wear on top of your jacket.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or, if you did not wear a jacket, on your shirt sleeves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could not go around without the yellow armband.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was-- that was the-- that was a must.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I remember one Purim.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's a holiday when [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it's permitted in our traditions to drink a little more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we had about 50 boys coming to our house, and they drank a little.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody became drunk, but they were somewhat high.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The first thing these these boys did was they ripped off, one by one, the yellow armband.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I recall this story always because there's a Talmudic teaching that [SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The wine goes in, and your-- the essence of your inner self comes to the surface.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I always mention this, that we are, first of all, a free nation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were always free.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Even if people enslaved us, there was no way that they could take our freedom, our emotional freedom, and the state of mind.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Our state of mind was always that of a free person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So here's a boy who is high, who is at ease.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead of like what other people would do when they are high-- they would use foul language.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would do all types of crazy things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The first thing he does is he rips off the yellow armband, because he is a Jewish boy, and he's a free boy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I also remember that as they left our home, they were in a good mood, and they did not want to put the yellow armband back on their sleeves.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
